'''喬許·莫斯奎拉-阿斯海姆'''（'''{{lang-en|Josh Mosqueira-Asheim}}'''），是[[桌上游戏|桌面游戏]]和[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]的设计师。曾擔任《[[暗黑破坏神III|暗黑破坏神III]]》的游戏总监。<ref name="d3-game-director" />

1996年，他开始设计游戏，当时他还是White Wolf的作家，他写《君士坦丁堡之夜》和《蒙特利尔之夜》时还在加拿大军队并读完大学。<ref name="d3-game-director">{{cite web | url=http://us.battle.net/d3/en/blog/9773963/ | title=Messages From Hell: The Future of Diablo III | publisher=Blizzard Entertainment | date=June 5, 2013 | author=Mosqueira, Josh | accessdate=2015-09-02 | archive-date=2016-07-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704173920/http://us.battle.net/d3/en/blog/9773963 | dead-url=no }}</ref> Mosqueira，菲尔•布勒和斯特凡•布罗设计游戏the Tribe 8和Dream Pod 9 <ref name="designers">{{Cite book|author=Shannon Appelcline|title=Designers & Dragons|publisher=Mongoose Publishing|year=2011| isbn= 978-1-907702-58-7|pages=273}}</ref>

Josh Mosqueira加入[[暴雪娱乐|暴雪娱乐]]并成为《暗黑破坏神III》的首席设计师，2013年6月他成为了《暗黑破坏神III》所有平台上的游戏总监<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2012/01/diablo-3-consoles/|title=Blizzard: Diablo III Is Coming To Consoles|accessdate=2012-01-11|publisher=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]|first=Jason|last=Schreier|date=2012-01-10|archive-date=2014-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140206155411/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2012/01/diablo-3-consoles/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 他曾是《[[英雄连|英雄连]]》的首席设计师<ref>{{cite journal|author=Scott, Ryan|date=July 2006|title=Company of Heroes: Dawn of (World) War (II)|journal=[[Computer_Gaming_World|Computer Gaming World]]|issue=264}}</ref>，2008年因为他参与《英雄连：抵抗前线》的工作而获得ELAN奖中的游戏创新奖<ref>{{cite news|author=Zacharias, Yvonne|date=2008-02-18|title=Mass Effect dominates as game of the year: Science fiction video, made by Edmonton company, cleans up at Elan Awards|newspaper=The Vancouver Sun|page=D1}}</ref>。2016年，從暴雪娛樂離職<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/7/1/12083496/unannounced-diablo-4-blizzard-hiring-new-game-director | title=Blizzard hiring new game director for unannounced Diablo project | work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] | publisher=Vox Media | first=Michael | last=McWhertor | date=July 1, 2016 | accessdate=July 2, 2016 | archive-date=2016-07-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701220320/http://www.polygon.com/2016/7/1/12083496/unannounced-diablo-4-blizzard-hiring-new-game-director | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

